usage-policy:
prefixes:
  ex: 'http://example.org/'
  wf: 'http://w3id.org/wellfort/ns/core#'
  spl: 'http://www.specialprivacy.eu/langs/usage-policy#'

DataSubjectPolicy:
  hasData: wf:Observation; wf:Patient
  hasProcessing: spl:AnyProcessing
  hasPurpose: spl:AnyPurpose
  hasRecipient: spl:AnyRecipient
  hasStorage:
    hasLocation: spl:AnyLocation
    hasDuration: spl:AnyDuration

DataControllerPolicy:
  hasData: spl:AnyData
  hasProcessing: spl:AnyProcessing
  hasPurpose: spl:AnyPurpose
  hasRecipient: spl:AnyRecipient
  hasStorage:
    hasLocation: spl:AnyLocation
    hasDuration: spl:AnyDuration
